								</p>
								<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
									<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3">
										<span class="font-medium">Duration:</span> 3-4 years
									</div>
									<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3">
										<span class="font-medium">Focus:</span> Comprehensive
									</div>
									<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3">
										<span class="font-medium">Placement:</span> Optional
									</div>
									<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3">
										<span class="font-medium">Study Abroad:</span> Available
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
